<p class="ayah 10-5" id="5" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the One Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَعَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">made</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلشَّمْسَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sun</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ضِيَآءً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a shining light,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْقَمَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the moon</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نُورًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a reflected light</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَدَّرَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and determined for it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَنَازِلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">phases,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِتَعْلَمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that you may know</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَدَدَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) number</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسِّنِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the years</span></span><span class="word staticWord">