<p class="ayah 10-6" id="6" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱخْتِلَـٰفِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) alternation</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّيْلِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the night</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلنَّهَارِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقَ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah has created</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَأَيَـٰتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) Signs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّقَوْمٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for a people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَتَّقُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who are God conscious.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>6<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 10-7" id="7" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرْجُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">expect</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِقَآءَنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the meeting with Us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَرَضُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and are pleased</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْحَيَوٲةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with the life</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلدُّنْيَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the world,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱطْمَأَنُّواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and feel satisfied</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span clas