<p class="ayah 10-8" id="8" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Those -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَأْوَٮٰهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their abode</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّارُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) the Fire,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they used (to)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَكْسِبُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">earn.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>8<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 10-9" id="9" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good deeds,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَهْدِيهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) guide them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبُّهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِإِيمَـٰنِهِمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by their faith.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Will flow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْتِهِمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">underneath them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the rivers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><sp