Word"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">between them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">concerning what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[therein]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَخْتَلِفُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they differ.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>19<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
