<p class="ayah 10-22" id="22" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the One Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُسَيِّرُكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">enables you to travel</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْبَرِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the land</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْبَحْرِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the sea,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you are</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْفُلْكِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the ships</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَجَرَيْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they sail</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ب