<p class="ayah 10-29" id="29" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَكَفَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So sufficient</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَهِيدَۢا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) a witness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَيْنَنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">between us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبَيْنَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and between you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِبَادَتِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your worship</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَغَـٰفِلِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">certainly unaware.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>29<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
