َ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلِيمُۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) All-Knower</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَفْعَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they do.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>36<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
