<p class="ayah 10-39" id="39" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Nay,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَّبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they denied</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُحِيطُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they could encompass</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِعِلْمِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) its knowledge</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَأْتِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has come (to) them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَأْوِيلُهُۥ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its interpretation.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَّبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">denied</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranTex