<p class="ayah 10-88" id="88" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالَ مُوسَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Musa said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Our Lord!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, You</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَاتَيْتَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">have given</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِرْعَوْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Firaun</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَلَأَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and his chiefs</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">زِينَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">splendor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَمْوَٲلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and wealth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَيَوٲةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the life</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلدُّنْيَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the world.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our Lord!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِيُضِلُّواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That they may lead astray</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلِكَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Your way.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our Lord!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱطْمِسْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Destroy</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْوَٲلِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their wealth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱشْدُدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and harden</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلُوبِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their hearts,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so (that) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُؤْمِنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرَوُاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعَذَابَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the punishment -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَلِيمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the painful."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>88<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 10-89" id="89" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">"Verily,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُجِيبَت</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has been answered</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَّعْوَتُكُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) invocation of both of you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱسْتَقِيمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So you two (keep to the) straight way.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَتَّبِعَآنِّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">follow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) way</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">know."</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>89<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
